Administration.name: Administration
Administration.description: Mod only commands! Nothing to see here!

commands.name: addquestions
commands.description:
aq (question)
adds a question to list, which are to be asked when scrutiny is turned one

commands.name: clearquestions
commands.description: Clears all question from list

commands.name: testquestions
commands.description: Sends a test question list to check!

commands.name: scrutiny
commands.description: Toggles scrutiny status!

commands.name: scrutinychannel
commands.description:
scrc 
sets channel where questions are to be asked

commands.name: eventchannel
commands.description:
evc 
sets channel where events will posted

commands.name: eventchannelconfig
commands.description:
evc 
Shows the channel where events will posted

commands.name: scrutinystatus
commands.description: Shows scrutiny status!

commands.name: filtermemberrole
commands.description:
scrr (role)
Sets the scrutiny role

commands.name: moderator
commands.description: Shows the list of mod roles, which are allowed to use these commands!

commands.name: addmoderator
commands.description:
addmods (role)
Adds the specified role to mod list!

commands.name: removemoderator
commands.description:
rmods (role)
Removes the role from mod list!

commands.name: lobbychannel
commands.description:
lbc (voice channel id or mention)
Sets the vc to create custom lobbies when joined!

commands.name: lobbystatus
commands.description: Shows custom lobbies status!

Bumper.name: Bump
Bumper.description: A type of bump leaderboard I guess!

commands.name: bumps
commands.description:
bumps (usermention)
Shows the bump of the user or the user itself who invoked the command!

commands.name: bumptop
commands.description: Shows the user who has bumped the server most times!

commands.name: setdomainchannel
commands.description: Sets domain channel for domain schedule messages!

commands.name: domainstatus
commands.description: Shows the domain channel set!

commands.name: domainlist
commands.description:
dlist (day)
Shows the domains rotation for a specific day!

commands.name: domainupdate
commands.description:
du (day)
Updates domain rotation according to day!

Fortune.name: Fortune
Fortune.description: Genshin Impact like fortune sticks implemented in discord!

commands.name: drawfortune
commands.description: Draws a fortune stick!

commands.name: openfortune
commands.description: Opens a fortune stick

Guides.name: Genshin Guides
Guides.description: Shows ascension or build guides of characters!

commands.name: build
commands.description:
b
Opens an interaction to choose character and see their builds

commands.name: ascension
commands.description:
as
Opens an interaction to choose character and see their Ascension

commands.name: addguide
commands.description:
addg (b or as)
Opens an interaction to add ascension or build guide!

commands.name: addcharacter
commands.description:
addc (character name)
Adds a character!

commands.name: hail
commands.description:
hail (usermention)
Shows a gif hailing the mentioned user!

Information.name: Information
Information.description: Provides general information and ascension materials required for basic genshin weapons and artifacts and characters!

commands.name: information
commands.description: Opens a interaction to get information about Genshin Impact weapons, and artifacts and characters

Lobbies.name: Lobby
Lobbies.description:
Commands to control and create custom lobbies
 ``!lb`` to check the lobby status!

commands.name: lobbyallow
commands.description:
la (usermention)
Allows the mentioned user to join your lobby!

commands.name: lobbykick
commands.description:
lk (usermention)
Kicks the mentioned member from your lobby!

commands.name: lobbyunallow
commands.description:
lua (usermention)
Prevents a member from joining your lobby!

commands.name: lobbylimit
commands.description:
ll (number or 0)
Limits the lobby to said number of members! or If given 0, set to 99!

commands.name: lobbylock
commands.description:
llock
Locks the lobby and make it private!

commands.name: lobbyunlock
commands.description:
lul
Unlocks the lobby and makes it public!

commands.name: lobbycreate
commands.description:
lc
Creates the lobby!

GenshinLogs.name: Genshin Logs
GenshinLogs.description: Fetches and shows the transaction logs of you Genshin Impact Account!

commands.name: genshinlogs
commands.description:
glogs (feedback link)
Fetches all logs of your account from feedback link!

commands.name: genshinprimogems
commands.description:
gprimogems (uid)
Shows primogems transactions of your genshin account!

commands.name: genshinartifacts
commands.description:
gartifacts (uid)
Shows artifacts transactions of your genshin account!

commands.name: genshincrystals
commands.description:
gcrystals (uid)
Shows crystals transactions of your genshin account!

commands.name: genshinresins
commands.description:
gresins (uid)
Shows resings transactions of your genshin account!

Notes.name: Guides Notes
Notes.description: Allows member to add notes, so they can add their suggestions to added builds!

commands.name: notes
commands.description:
Opens an interaction to see the added notes!
Only the original creator can delete the note!

commands.name: addnotes
commands.description: Opens an interaction to add a note!

commands.name: ping
commands.description: Shows the your and bot delay

QuestsWalkthrough.name: Quests
QuestsWalkthrough.description: Commands to get details of acts, quests and chapters

commands.name: quests
commands.description:
quest (chapter | act | quest name)
Shows the quests in a chapter | act
 If a quest is mentioned, shows quest details
if none mentioned shows all the quests!

commands.name: acts
commands.description:
act (act name)
Shows the quests in a act or if none mentioned shows all the acts!

commands.name: chapters
commands.description:
chapter (chapter name)
Shows the acts in a chapter or if none mentioned shows all the chapters!

SoundBoard.name: Soundboard
SoundBoard.description: Commands to play sounds of different characters

commands.name: soundboardcharacters
commands.description:
sbc
Opens an interaction to play a sound for user

commands.name: soundboardpaimon
commands.description:
sbp
Plays the available paimon sounds in vc!

UIDManager.name: UID Manager
UIDManager.description:
Commands for Genshin Impact Profiles
 <#889200292418187316> is channel where user can drop their uids and get them linked!

commands.name: genshinlink
commands.description:
glink (uid)
Links the UID and Region with the user!

commands.name: gserver
commands.description:
gserv (user `optional`)
Shows the linked uids of a user or either the user who has invoked the command

commands.name: genshinuid
commands.description:
guid (uid)
shows the discord user which has linked the uid!

commands.name: genshincharacters
commands.description:
gchar (region) (member `optional`)
Shows the most used characters of a user from genshin api!

commands.name: genshinstats
commands.description:
gstat (region)
Shows the stat of a user genshin impact account!

commands.name: genshinabyss
commands.description:
gabyss (region)
Shows the abyss stats of a user genshin impact account!

commands.name: resinstatus
commands.description:
rs (region)
Shows your resin status!

commands.name: resintime
commands.description:
rt (region)
Shows your remaining time for resin to fill up!

commands.name: resinreminder
commands.description:
rr (region) (resin)
Shows your resin status!

WishHistory.name: Genshin Wish history
WishHistory.description: Fetches your wish history from Mihoyo grasp, calculate pity for you!

commands.name: wishhistory
commands.description:
wh (wishhistory url)
Fetches wish history for user
Provide the link to outputlog.txt file or the wish history link from game!

commands.name: wishshow
commands.description:
ws (uid) (bannercode)
Shows wish history for provided arguments
 if no banner code is provided, prints all the available banner codes!

commands.name: wishimagesave
commands.description:
Mod only command
resaves all images according to template!

lext( extension name)
Loads extension

commands.name: uloadext
commands.description:
unlext( extension name)
Unloads extension

commands.name: rloadext

lext( extension name)
Reloads extension
